            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">к нашим соседям приехали гости</q>
            </tr>
            <tr xml:lang="en">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">guests came to our neighbours</q>
